Name: ConnectWise 1.0.0.1
Message:
Welcome to the ConnectWise REST Connector for SmartConnect.

The connector was built using v4_6_release of the ConnectWise codebase.

The official documentation for ConnectWise web services can be found here.

*A free developer account is required to access the documentation.

Installation

After importing the REST Connector definition from the JSON file, you will need to configure the connector.  

There are 6 required fields on the connector setup to configure.

FieldDescription
UsernameCompanyName+Public API Key
PasswordPrivate API Key
ClientIdClientId Generated Here
versionDefault is 2022.1
VersionNumberTested on v4_6_release
ConnectWiseSiteBased on your region

Once you have collected all the information above you can enter it in the setup so it looks like the below screenshot.

GenericRestParameters.Name: conditions
GenericRestParameters.Value: lastUpdated>=[GBL_CW_DATE] and updatedBy !='[[integrationUser]]' and deletedFlag=false and isVendorFlag=true

Actions.Name: Create Project

Lookups.Name: Invoice Payment Id by Invoice Id
Unit of Measure Id by Name
